294
00:14:49,740 --> 00:14:51,140
I believed in you.

295
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:53,460
But now it's different.

296
00:14:54,820 --> 00:14:55,900
Gong is gone.

297
00:14:56,500 --> 00:14:57,540
You're all I have left.

298
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:00,340
No matter what,

299
00:15:00,980 --> 00:15:02,340
I won't let anything happen to you.

300
00:15:04,820 --> 00:15:05,700
I know

301
00:15:06,500 --> 00:15:08,140
I'm not as capable as Gong.

302
00:15:08,740 --> 00:15:10,220
But I'll give it everything I've got.

303
00:15:10,540 --> 00:15:11,980
I'll do whatever you ask.

304
00:15:12,540 --> 00:15:14,220
Just give me a little time.

305
00:15:14,940 --> 00:15:16,340
Even if it's just a little while.

306
00:15:17,500 --> 00:15:18,620
Please, just trust me.

307
00:15:43,020 --> 00:15:44,060
You're right.

308
00:15:45,980 --> 00:15:47,340
Your brother's gone.

309
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:50,660
You're the only son I have now.

310
00:15:54,740 --> 00:15:57,020
Prove yourself to him,

311
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,340
and carry out my final wish.

312
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,140
Understood, Dad.

313
00:16:49,540 --> 00:16:50,340
You, come over here!

314
00:16:55,820 --> 00:16:56,500
Still flinching?

315
00:16:59,100 --> 00:16:59,820
Let's go in.

316
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:02,180
Talk about bad luck.

317
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:04,060
His brother owed money

318
00:17:04,620 --> 00:17:05,660
and then died.

319
00:17:06,060 --> 00:17:07,140
Now he's stuck with the debt.

320
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:09,060
Out of nowhere, he's got a bill to pay.

321
00:17:09,060 --> 00:17:10,060
Unlucky doesn't even begin to cover it.

322
00:17:10,420 --> 00:17:12,580
Bad luck? He's got nothing
on his cousin, Ma San-po.

323
00:17:14,180 --> 00:17:15,060
Ma San-po?

324
00:17:17,100 --> 00:17:17,860
What do they want?

325
00:17:18,020 --> 00:17:19,220
Debts must be paid, of course.

326
00:17:21,020 --> 00:17:22,940
They told him to help deliver goods
to pay off the debt.

327
00:17:23,340 --> 00:17:24,300
That brat

328
