350
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:30,220
Take it back to the cell.

351
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:31,340
Wait till I come for you.

352
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:46,420
So, you're the judge's son, huh?

353
00:18:48,940 --> 00:18:49,820
