354
00:18:53,540 --> 00:18:54,820
A gust of wind would knock him over.

355
00:18:55,900 --> 00:18:56,660
Get up.

356
00:18:57,020 --> 00:18:57,980
So useless.

357
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:58,740
