358
00:18:58,740 --> 00:18:59,420
What are you doing?

359
00:18:59,420 --> 00:18:59,980
Behave yourselves.

360
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:01,060
Watch yourself.

361
00:19:01,460 --> 00:19:02,100
Forget it.

362
00:19:02,660 --> 00:19:03,100
Go.

363
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:05,740
Are you okay?

364
