I'm fine.

365
00:19:07,180 --> 00:19:07,820
Stop.

366
00:19:16,860 --> 00:19:17,740
Did he really do it?

367
00:19:18,620 --> 00:19:20,140
Hearing that guy's Ma San-po's cousin,

368
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:22,180
