369
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:50,340
How did your arm get hurt?

370
00:19:51,940 --> 00:19:52,740
It's nothing.

371
00:19:53,740 --> 00:19:54,540
Stop.

372
00:20:00,100 --> 00:20:01,060
