376
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:09,980
The warden told us
to take good care of you.

377
00:20:12,340 --> 00:20:12,820
Go.

378
00:20:17,100 --> 00:20:17,900
I was being careless.

379
00:20:21,540 --> 00:20:22,900
I know it's tough in here.

380
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:25,380
Even out here,

381
00:20:26,140 --> 00:20:27,620
I keep telling myself

382
00:20:28,460 --> 00:20:29,740
it'll end someday.

383
00:20:30,900 --> 00:20:31,500
Yat-wai,

384
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:32,940
hang in there.

385
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:37,460
I brought you some books.

386
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:39,020
No need.

387
00:20:40,100 --> 00:20:41,540
Grandma already brought me a lot.

388
00:20:43,540 --> 00:20:44,140
That's right.

389
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:46,420
She and I both think

390
00:20:46,900 --> 00:20:48,500
