397
00:21:01,580 --> 00:21:02,260
Sometimes

398
00:21:03,100 --> 00:21:04,540
I think about his face.

399
00:21:06,500 --> 00:21:08,060
Shouldn't we be looking ahead?

400
00:21:12,380 --> 00:21:13,140
Here,

401
00:21:13,180 --> 00:21:14,180
they all call me

402
00:21:14,260 --> 00:21:15,260
the judge's son.

403
00:21:16,260 --> 00:21:16,860
But the truth is,

404
00:21:17,420 --> 00:21:18,780
I'm no different from them.

405
00:21:19,980 --> 00:21:20,740
We're all just prisoners.

406
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:23,340
Dad,

407
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:25,420
I've grown up.

408
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:26,900
I can take care of myself.

409
00:22:11,380 --> 00:22:13,460
A knife wound,

410
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,420
curled like an earthworm.

411
00:22:16,900 --> 00:22:19,260
Clearly, the result of stitching.

412
00:22:19,900 --> 00:22:20,780
You're asking

413
00:22:20,820 --> 00:22:22,060
if anyone would remember

414
00:22:22,300 --> 00:22:24,060
whether he really went to the hospital

415
00:22:24,580 --> 00:22:25,580
for treatment?

416
00:22:25,660 --> 00:22:26,340
Exactly.

417
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,540
Huen, stop fooling around.

418
00:22:29,980 --> 00:22:31,660
That was 20 years ago.

419
00:22:32,740 --> 00:22:34,780
I know I can't check

420
00:22:34,820 --> 00:22:36,980
every hospital's files from back then.

421
00:22:37,300 --> 00:22:38,420
But I can ask, can't I?

422
00:22:39,020 --> 00:22:40,300
With your connections,

423
00:22:40,540 --> 00:22:42,020
maybe I really can find out

424
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:44,180
if there was a doctor or nurse

425
00:22:44,500 --> 00:22:45,980
who did that kind of surgery.

426
00:22:46,380 --> 00:22:48,100
They might still remember the person.

427
00:22:50,580 --> 00:22:51,740
Is this evidence important?

428
00:22:54,300 --> 00:22:55,380
It might be

429
00:22:56,180 --> 00:22:57,900
evidence to clear Sek's name.

430
00:23:03,100 --> 00:23:03,620
Understood.

431
00:23:07,100 --> 00:23:07,860
I'll help you.

432
00:23:14,060 --> 00:23:15,020
Your blood pressure's a little high.

433
00:23:15,340 --> 00:23:16,420
I'd recommend cutting back on alcohol.

434
00:23:16,780 --> 00:23:17,900
Now that I'm out on medical parole,

435
00:23:18,140 --> 00:23:19,700
I need a condition you can treat.

436
00:23:21,100 --> 00:23:22,460
Lung, please get some proper rest.

437
00:23:26,060 --> 00:23:26,580
Lung.

438
00:23:29,220 --> 00:23:30,340
Weren't you feeling sick earlier?

439
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:32,740
Let me call the doctor back
to check on you.

440
00:23:33,180 --> 00:23:34,300
I'm fine, Lung.

441
00:23:35,700 --> 00:23:37,020
Yesterday was the anniversary
of my brother's death.

442
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,380
He was only six when he passed away.

443
00:23:47,500 --> 00:23:48,700
Don't dwell

444
00:23:49,620 --> 00:23:50,620
