445
00:23:52,140 --> 00:23:53,180
But every time I see you,

446
00:23:54,620 --> 00:23:55,660
I can't help but think about it.

447
00:23:58,540 --> 00:23:59,380
What do you mean?

448
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:03,500
Twenty years ago, the shantytown fire

449
00:24:04,580 --> 00:24:06,220
killed my entire family.

450
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:09,540
But on that very night,

451
00:24:10,100 --> 00:24:10,860
I met you.

452
00:24:12,300 --> 00:24:13,340
I still remember.

453
00:24:13,340 --> 00:24:14,020
I found you

454
00:24:14,540 --> 00:24:15,940
squatting by the road,

455
00:24:17,020 --> 00:24:17,980
totally bewildered

456
00:24:18,860 --> 00:24:20,380
and weeping until your eyes were puffy.

457
00:24:23,540 --> 00:24:24,060
Lung,

458
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:26,380
