462
00:24:40,300 --> 00:24:40,780
Lung,

463
00:24:41,100 --> 00:24:42,300
I found this leather jacket.

464
00:24:42,340 --> 00:24:43,140
Do you remember it?

465
00:24:44,980 --> 00:24:46,340
On the night we met,

466
00:24:46,340 --> 00:24:47,780
