467
00:24:49,140 --> 00:24:50,060
You still kept it?

468
00:24:50,700 --> 00:24:51,820
It holds some memories, doesn't it?

469
00:24:54,180 --> 00:24:55,700
Let's see if it still fits me.

470
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:12,980
It does.

471
00:25:13,260 --> 00:25:14,220
Feels just right.

472
00:25:14,580 --> 00:25:15,380
Lung.

473
00:25:17,300 --> 00:25:18,540
You and Lit

474
00:25:18,780 --> 00:25:20,500
are the only family I have left.

475
00:25:21,900 --> 00:25:23,020
Is there something you want to tell me?

476
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:29,740
Yes.

477
00:25:32,860 --> 00:25:33,860
I appreciate you

478
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:35,500
helping me look after my two sons

479
00:25:35,820 --> 00:25:37,380
these past twenty years.

480
00:25:41,740 --> 00:25:42,300
And...

481
00:25:44,060 --> 00:25:44,860
what do you feel like eating?

482
00:25:45,780 --> 00:25:46,620
I'll send someone to pick it up.

483
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:09,220
[Sek Chi-yeung]

484
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:19,420
[Fu-Ngam Shantytown arson.
Sek Chi-yeung]

485
00:26:43,580 --> 00:26:44,300
Lo Keung,

486
00:26:45,140 --> 00:26:46,940
you've been by my side
for 20 years, right?

487
00:26:47,620 --> 00:26:48,340
Twenty-one years, actually.

488
00:26:55,180 --> 00:26:56,660
We'll talk here.

489
00:26:57,500 --> 00:26:58,340
Go wait over there.

490
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:09,060
I didn't expect

491
00:27:10,660 --> 00:27:12,300
that now I can't even boss around

492
00:27:12,540 --> 00:27:13,660
my two subordinates.

493
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:16,100
Mr. Hon Lit asked us

494
00:27:16,540 --> 00:27:17,980
