495
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:19,780
So tell me. Whom do you answer?

496
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:21,660
Him, or me?

497
00:27:30,260 --> 00:27:31,540
Don't be nervous.

498
00:27:34,140 --> 00:27:35,820
Having you by his side

499
00:27:35,820 --> 00:27:37,100
