503
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:47,460
I'm proud of what Lit's become.

504
00:27:49,700 --> 00:27:50,940
Even if he

505
00:27:51,340 --> 00:27:52,580
takes over the family,

506
00:27:53,260 --> 00:27:54,260
I'm fine with that.

507
00:27:56,580 --> 00:27:58,540
Our family must carry on and thrive.

508
00:28:01,700 --> 00:28:03,100
But my son is gone.

509
00:28:03,980 --> 00:28:05,380
Someone has to pay with their life.

510
00:28:08,180 --> 00:28:09,860
That judge must die.

511
00:28:12,380 --> 00:28:13,460
I know what to do.

512
00:28:15,380 --> 00:28:16,580
No one else will ever know about this.

513
00:28:36,140 --> 00:28:36,780
Mr. Wu,

514
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:39,940
can you respect personal boundaries?

515
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:42,980
If I didn't,

516
00:28:42,980 --> 00:28:44,860
I would've aired your dirty laundry
a long time ago.

517
00:28:46,100 --> 00:28:47,100
What did I do?

518
00:28:47,860 --> 00:28:49,780
I've had two hospitals reach out,

519
00:28:50,100 --> 00:28:52,180
reporting that you meddled
in their work.

520
00:28:53,180 --> 00:28:54,660
I was only in their way

