00:29:30,780 --> 00:29:31,460
Mr. Tat.

537
00:29:34,700 --> 00:29:35,980
Freshly baked egg tarts.

538
00:29:35,980 --> 00:29:37,100
Lung hasn't had them in a long time.

539
00:29:38,060 --> 00:29:39,180
