563
00:30:26,940 --> 00:30:27,980
Drop the nonsense.

564
00:30:29,140 --> 00:30:29,860
Get to the point.

565
00:30:30,180 --> 00:30:31,180
Here's the deal.

566
00:30:32,180 --> 00:30:33,580
Burning down the shantytown

567
00:30:33,580 --> 00:30:35,540
